Package ca.cgjennings.spelling.dict

Class TernaryTreeList.TTLInfo

java.lang.Object
ca.cgjennings.spelling.dict.TernaryTreeList.TTLInfo
Enclosing class:
TernaryTreeList
public static final class TernaryTreeList.TTLInfo extends Object
Some simple statistical data that can be obtained quickly from a ternary tree word list. This is returned by TernaryTreeList.getInfo(java.io.File). It can be useful to present this information in a dictionary management interface, to help the user identify different versions of a dictionary.
